#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:2
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:4
msgid ""
"LMCache multiprocess (MP) mode runs LMCache as a **standalone service** "
"that vLLM instances connect to over ZMQ.  One LMCache server per node can"
" serve multiple vLLM pods, providing process isolation, shared caching, "
"and independent resource scaling."
msgstr ""
"LMCache 多进程 (MP) 模式将 LMCache 作为一个 **独立服务** 运行，vLLM 实例通过 ZMQ 连接到该服务。每个节点的 "
"LMCache 服务器可以为多个 vLLM pod 提供服务，提供进程隔离、共享缓存和独立资源扩展。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:14
msgid "Key Benefits"
msgstr "主要优势"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:16
msgid ""
"**Process isolation** -- LMCache and vLLM run in separate processes (or "
"containers), so a cache-related issue does not crash the inference "
"engine."
msgstr "**进程隔离** -- LMCache 和 vLLM 在独立的进程（或容器）中运行，因此与缓存相关的问题不会导致推理引擎崩溃。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:18
msgid ""
"**No GIL contention or Python overhead on the inference path** -- By "
"running LMCache in a separate process, its Python GIL and CPU work "
"(hashing, memory management, L2 I/O) do not compete with vLLM's inference"
" threads."
msgstr ""
"**推理路径上没有 GIL 争用或 Python 开销** -- 通过在单独的进程中运行 LMCache，它的 Python GIL 和 CPU "
"工作（哈希、内存管理、L2 I/O）不会与 vLLM 的推理线程竞争。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:21
msgid ""
"**Shared caching across pods** -- Multiple vLLM instances on the same "
"node share a single L1 cache, maximizing KV reuse."
msgstr "**跨 Pod 共享缓存** -- 同一节点上的多个 vLLM 实例共享一个 L1 缓存，最大化 KV 重用。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:23
msgid ""
"**Independent resource scaling** -- Allocate CPU memory for caching "
"independently of GPU memory for inference."
msgstr "**独立资源扩展** -- 为缓存分配 CPU 内存，与用于推理的 GPU 显存独立。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:25
msgid ""
"**Multi-tier storage (L1 + L2)** -- An L1 cache (in CPU DRAM, or an NVMe "
"slab via GPUDirect Storage) backed by persistent L2 storage via NIXL "
"(GDS, POSIX, HF3FS, and more)."
msgstr ""
"**多层存储 (L1 + L2)** -- 一个 L1 缓存（在 CPU DRAM 中，或通过 GPUDirect Storage 的 NVMe "
"块）由通过 NIXL（GDS、POSIX、HF3FS 等）支持的持久 L2 存储。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:28
msgid ""
"**Built-in observability** -- Prometheus metrics and a telemetry event "
"system out of the box."
msgstr "**内置可观察性** -- 开箱即用的 Prometheus 指标和遥测事件系统。"

