msgid "``PREPARE_STORE``"
msgstr "``PREPARE_STORE``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:185
msgid ""
"(Engine-driven path) Worker asks the server to prepare store-side "
"transfer state for a key. Loaded when ``--supported-transfer-mode`` is "
"``engine_driven`` or ``auto``."
msgstr ""
"（引擎驱动路径）工作线程请求服务器为一个键准备存储端传输状态。当 ``--supported-transfer-mode`` 设置为 "
