#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:188
msgid "``COMMIT_STORE``"
msgstr "``COMMIT_STORE``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:190
msgid ""
"(Engine-driven path) Worker commits the chunk's serialized bytes (pickle "
"path) or releases the prepared SHM slot (SHM path) so the server can "
"persist into L1 storage."
msgstr "(引擎驱动路径) 工作线程提交块的序列化字节（pickle 路径）或释放准备好的共享内存槽（SHM 路径），以便服务器可以持久化到 L1 存储。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:193
msgid "``PREPARE_RETRIEVE``"
msgstr "``PREPARE_RETRIEVE``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:195
msgid ""
"(Engine-driven path) Worker asks the server to prepare the retrieval "
"payload for a key. The pickle path returns the bytes inline; the SHM path"
" returns slot info so the worker can read from shared memory."
msgstr "（引擎驱动路径）工作线程请求服务器为一个键准备检索负载。pickle 路径在线返回字节；SHM 路径返回槽位信息，以便工作线程可以从共享内存中读取。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:199
msgid "``COMMIT_RETRIEVE``"
msgstr "``COMMIT_RETRIEVE``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:201
msgid ""
"(Engine-driven path) Worker acknowledges retrieval completion so the "
"server can release the underlying read locks and reclaim any transport "
"state."
msgstr "(引擎驱动路径) 工作线程确认检索完成，以便服务器可以释放底层读取锁并回收任何传输状态。"

