msgstr "(Blend) 查找预计算段块。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:252
msgid "``CB_RETRIEVE_PRE_COMPUTED``"
msgstr "``CB_RETRIEVE_PRE_COMPUTED``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:254
msgid "(Blend) Retrieve pre-computed paragraph chunks to GPU."
msgstr "(Blend) 将预计算的段落块检索到 GPU。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:255
msgid "``CB_STORE_FINAL``"
msgstr "``CB_STORE_FINAL``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:257
msgid "(Blend) Store final blended chunks."
msgstr "(Blend) 存储最终混合块。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:258
msgid "``CB_LOOKUP_PRE_COMPUTED_V2``"
msgstr "``CB_LOOKUP_PRE_COMPUTED_V2``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:260
msgid ""
"(Blend V2) Lookup pre-computed chunks; returns ``CBMatchResult`` entries "
"(with old/cur ranges and per-chunk hashes) so the retrieve step can skip "
"re-hashing."
msgstr "（Blend V2）查找预计算块；返回 ``CBMatchResult`` 条目（包含旧范围/当前范围和每块哈希），以便检索步骤可以跳过重新哈希。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:263
msgid "``CB_RETRIEVE_PRE_COMPUTED_V2``"
msgstr "``CB_RETRIEVE_PRE_COMPUTED_V2``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:265
msgid ""
"(Blend V2) Retrieve pre-computed chunks using the ``CBMatchResult`` list "
"returned by ``CB_LOOKUP_PRE_COMPUTED_V2``."
msgstr ""
"（Blend V2）使用 ``CB_LOOKUP_PRE_COMPUTED_V2`` 返回的 ``CBMatchResult`` "
"列表检索预计算的块。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:267
msgid "``CB_REGISTER_ROPE_V3``"
msgstr "``CB_REGISTER_ROPE_V3``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:269
msgid ""
"(Blend V3) Share the RoPE cos/sin cache onto a context already registered"
" via ``REGISTER_KV_CACHE``."
msgstr "(Blend V3) 将 RoPE cos/sin 缓存共享到已经通过 ``REGISTER_KV_CACHE`` 注册的上下文中。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:271
msgid "``CB_UNREGISTER_ROPE_V3``"
msgstr "``CB_UNREGISTER_ROPE_V3``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:273
msgid ""
"(Blend V3) Drop the RoPE state (paged KV cache lives on; use "
"``UNREGISTER_KV_CACHE`` to release that)."
msgstr "(Blend V3) 丢弃 RoPE 状态（分页 KV Cache 仍然存在；使用 ``UNREGISTER_KV_CACHE`` 来释放它）。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:275
msgid "``CB_RETRIEVE_PRE_COMPUTED_V3``"
msgstr "``CB_RETRIEVE_PRE_COMPUTED_V3``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:277
msgid ""
"(Blend V3) Scatter all matched chunks (prefix- and non-prefix-hit) into "
"paged KV by per-token block ID; re-RoPE only the shifted subset."
msgstr "（Blend V3）将所有匹配的块（前缀命中和非前缀命中）按每个令牌块 ID 散布到分页 KV 中；仅对移动的子集进行重新 RoPE。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:279
msgid "``CB_UNIFIED_LOOKUP``"
msgstr "``CB_UNIFIED_LOOKUP``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:281
msgid ""
"(Blend V3) Sole live lookup path: one RPC runs prefix + non-prefix match,"
" reconciles, issues one sparse-coalesced prefetch, and classifies per-TP-"
"rank. Returns ``CBUnifiedLookupResult`` (or ``None`` while the prefetch "
"is still in flight)."
msgstr ""
"（Blend V3）唯一的实时查找路径：一个 RPC 运行前缀 + 非前缀匹配，进行协调，发出一个稀疏合并的预取，并按每个 TP 排名分类。返回 "
"``CBUnifiedLookupResult``（或者在预取仍在进行中时返回 ``None``）。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:285
msgid "``P2P_LOOKUP_AND_LOCK``"
msgstr "``P2P_LOOKUP_AND_LOCK``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:287
msgid ""
"(P2P) Look up the given keys and read-lock the locally cached prefix. "
"Returns a task id which the caller passes to ``P2P_QUERY_LOOKUP_RESULTS``"
" to poll for the transfer addresses. Part of the peer-to-peer KV cache "
"sharing surface; the handler module is not yet wired into the default "
"``_build_modules()`` path -- see :doc:`p2p`."
msgstr "(P2P) 查找给定的键并对本地缓存的前缀进行读锁定。返回一个任务 ID，调用者将其传递给 ``P2P_QUERY_LOOKUP_RESULTS`` 以轮询传输地址。是点对点 KV Cache 共享接口的一部分；处理程序模块尚未连接到默认的 ``_build_modules()`` 路径 -- 请参见 :doc:`p2p`。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:293
msgid "``P2P_QUERY_LOOKUP_RESULTS``"
msgstr "``P2P_QUERY_LOOKUP_RESULTS``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:295
msgid ""
"(P2P) Poll the transfer addresses for a lookup task. Returns a list of "
"``TransferChannelAddress`` once the lookup is complete, or ``None`` while"
" the lookup is still in progress or its results have already been "
"consumed."
msgstr "(P2P) 查询查找任务的传输地址。查找完成后返回一个 ``TransferChannelAddress`` 列表，或者在查找仍在进行中或其结果已被消费时返回 ``None``。"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:299
msgid "``P2P_UNLOCK_OBJECTS``"
msgstr "``P2P_UNLOCK_OBJECTS``"

#: ../../source/mp/index.rst:301
msgid ""
"(P2P) Release the read locks previously taken by ``P2P_LOOKUP_AND_LOCK`` "
"on the given keys."
msgstr "(P2P) 释放之前由 ``P2P_LOOKUP_AND_LOCK`` 在给定键上获取的读锁。"

